title: Cant see my clan
body: My club has been messed up ever since the bug first started months ago. I am the leader and i cant see it, use the tag, or disband it. May i get some help. The club is called Kya Army, and the tag is (Kya)

replies.body: I hit a button from our side that may have resolved this. Let me know if you still encounter issues with this!
